 words can be!"},{"kind":"text","text":" But what does your rebuke prove?"}],"crossRefs":[],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:6:26","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"Do you think that you can disprove my words"},{"kind":"text","text":" or that a despairing man’s words are mere wind? "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 8:2","book":"Job","chapter":8,"verse":2,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 15:2","book":"Job","chapter":15,"verse":2,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 16:3","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":3,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 8:2","book":"Job","chapter":8,"verse":2},{"label":"Jb 15:2","book":"Job","chapter":15,"verse":2},{"label":"Jb 16:3","book":"Job","chapter":16,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:6:27","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"No doubt you would cast lots for a fatherless child"},{"kind":"text","text":" and negotiate a price to sell your friend. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jl 3:3","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":3,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Nah 3:10","book":"Nam","chapter":3,"verse":10,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"2Pt 2:3","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":3,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jl 3:3","book":"Jol","chapter":3,"verse":3},{"label":"Nah 3:10","book":"Nam","chapter":3,"verse":10},{"label":"2Pt 2:3","book":"2Pe","chapter":2,"verse":3}],"footnotes":[]},{"verseId":"a556c5305ee15c3f-01:Job:6:28","parts":[{"kind":"text","text":"But now, please look at me;"},{"kind":"text","text":" I will not lie to your face. "},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 24:25","book":"Job","chapter":24,"verse":25,"letter":"a"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 27:4","book":"Job","chapter":27,"verse":4,"letter":"b"},{"kind":"crossref","label":"Jb 34:6","book":"Job","chapter":34,"verse":6,"letter":"c"}],"crossRefs":[{"label":"Jb 24:25","book":"Job","chapter":24,"verse":25},{"label":"Jb 27:4","book":"Job","chapter":27,"verse":4},{"label":"Jb 34:6","book":"Job","cha